    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Wilkes Barre</placeName>
                <date>Aug 31<hi rend="sup">st</hi> 1850</date>
            </p>
            <p><addressee>Rev: I: Leeser</addressee>!</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">DSir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Yours Respectfully<lb/> by the hand of our <sic>frind</sic>
                <persName>Mr Allen</persName> is<lb/> Received, and contents noticed.<lb/> I have
                    <sic>collect-it</sic> from <persName>H. Ansbacher</persName> $3.00</p>
            <p><persName>S. Ullmann</persName>     .      .     .     .                 <hi
                    rend="underline">4.00</hi></p>
            <p rend="align(right)">making 9.00</p>
            <p>The balance for the Oc: I will try &amp;<lb/> collect this week, I have also
                sold.<lb/> Two of the Prayer Books, &amp; could sell<lb/> a few more, by sending
                them soon.<lb/> You may send also 1 Doz of Books.<lb/> for young Sunday Scholars,
                which you know<lb/> the best to take, to <sic>comence</sic> a Sunday<lb/> School
                with.</p>
            <p>I will <del>enter</del> try &amp; collect the whole amount<lb/> due you, with the
                    <sic>acception</sic> of <persName>M. Lang</persName>,<lb/> which I am
                    <sic>sarow</sic> to inform you is a<lb/> bad case.—</p>
            <p>Your Sermon was left with <persName>M. Lang</persName><lb/> and I shall try to
                    <sic>git</sic> it from <sic>hime</sic>,<lb/> You must excuse, of my
                    <sic>neglegt</sic>, I<lb/> have been from home, and <sic>werry</sic>
                <sic>busely</sic></p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>engaged. I will promise you to do<lb/> better in future.</p>
            <p>Should you <add>?</add> a Paper, I will <sic>git</sic> subscribers<lb/> for a weekly
                or daily Paper, and do all<lb/> I. can for you.</p>
            <p>Wishing you a happy new year.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I. remain, Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Respectfully, Your</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">obt—Servant</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">M. W. Strouse</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <addressee>Rev: I. Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Phila<hi rend="underline">da</hi></placeName>
            </p>
            <p><sic>Politness</sic> of</p>
            <p>
                <persName>Mr Allen</persName>
            </p>
